dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents buildings for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2010.[Building Footprints were created using 2005 LiDAR raster math and ENVI 4.8. Features were extracted and simplified in Arcmap. Features were manually added in the clean up process to match the 2010 Aerial Photography.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
